
## ─────── VS Code Dark Nano Theme (macOS-safe) ───────

## Load syntax definitions
include ~/.nano/*.nanorc

## Basic behavior
set linenumbers
set softwrap
set tabsize 4
set autoindent
set mouse

## Simple color tweaks
set titlecolor brightwhite,blue
set statuscolor brightwhite,black
set selectedcolor black,white
set numbercolor cyan

## Make comments, strings, etc. visible through syntax files
# (colors defined inside the .nanorc language files)

## Important: use a dark terminal background (like "Pro" or "Tango Dark")
